Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}繪畫你的笑顏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:42.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能坦白面對的瞬間
