Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================TEXT================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 我不在還是感覺很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要請我吃那件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那個打到了會非常疼的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:49.62,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(336,533)}決戰! 班級對抗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能防住第一下 還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我教你的無反作用力迴旋攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去只會變成消耗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是先拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的只是刺拳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的攻擊 是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是衝擊炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空間本體上施加壓力生成炮身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的藍色之淚一樣 是第三世代兵器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真會躲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這個龍炮的特徵就是炮身和炮彈都看不見的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個衝擊炮 在射擊角度上幾乎也沒有限制的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說沒有射擊死角的意思麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快想點辦法取得主動權的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去就輸定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想 我可是拿著和千冬姐一樣的武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白式的武器只有這個雪片貳型麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是只靠這個獲得優勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有它一個就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我和世界大賽優勝者相提並論好嗎 我很為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來像你這樣的外行人 能夠參加射擊戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反作用力制御 從彈道的預測到拉開距離的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬時停止 特殊無反作用力迴旋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 將炮彈的特性 大氣的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及與對手武裝的相互影響都考慮在內的思考型戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都能辦得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比較適合將一件事情專精上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護罩無效化攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要認真的上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你看看什麼叫做不是一個級別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學 好像有什麼打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瞬時加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我教他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬時加速？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間達到最高速度 接近敵人的奇襲攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要發動時機沒有問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也可以和代表候補生抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使用的次數只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊打偏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統破損
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明來源的攻擊將競技場的護盾破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽中止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 凰 給我立刻迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 比賽中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快躲到底座去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所屬不明的IS？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鎖定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙把我鎖定了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 趕緊到底座去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁那個時候 你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能丟下女生一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是因為你比較弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有要和它戰到最後的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對這種異常事態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園的老師們會立刻趕來處理…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束兵器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且比起塞西莉亞的IS來輸出功率更高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 笨蛋 快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 喂 別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}吵死了吵死了吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋 別打了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的也能叫做IS嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學 凰同學 請立刻離開競技場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師會馬上用IS進行壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 必須在大家離開之前 攔住這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧 鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你以為你在跟誰說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 你先放開我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是動不了了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方好像幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 我來做掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的武器只有那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就這麼幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 織斑同學 織斑同學聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凰同學聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們本人都說了要戰鬥 就讓他們試試看也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織 織斑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能說得這麼輕鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 喝點咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為糖分不足才會那麼焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 老師 那個是鹽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 請給我IS的使用許可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以立刻出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很想那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過先看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔離防護罩被設定成等級4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且所有的門都被鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那台IS做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 不論是要避難還是要救援都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門鎖著了 誰來開門啦 這裡也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 作為緊急事態向政府尋求援助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在三年級的精銳正在強行進入系統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能解除隔離防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會立刻讓部隊突入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我們就只能等待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正無論如何都不會讓你參加突擊隊的 你安下心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的藍色之淚裝備適合以一敵多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在多對一的情況下會反而會礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說我礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我問你 你參加過連攜訓練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你的分工是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方的組成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人是假定在什麼等級
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體的連續運作時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道了啦 已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏你給我等等 好好瞄準啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都已經是第四回了誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有在瞄準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護罩無效化攻擊只能再使用一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 後退！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想好一個作戰方案的話 是打不過它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃的話逃走也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是代表候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 那我也守護好你的背後給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 鈴 不覺得那傢伙的動作有點機械麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你在說什麼啊 IS本來就是機械啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……真的有人坐在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 沒人的話IS是動不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始 那傢伙就在我們說話的時候不太發動攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿是很有興趣地在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不可能是無人機的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS沒有人搭乘的話絕對是動不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是那樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設 只是假設而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是無人機的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 無人機的話就能打敗它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果裡面沒有人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算毫不客氣地全力攻擊也無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零落白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪片貳型的全力攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪片貳型的威力恐怕是高得過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練或校內對戰時使出全力是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若對方是無人機的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使全力攻擊也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零落白夜什麼的我是不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊本身不是就打不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就能打到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得板上釘釘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們就假設那是無人機攻擊看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我一打暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就以衝擊炮朝那傢伙攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最大威力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 不過打不中的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打不中也沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就立刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的話 連那種程度的敵人都贏不了 成何體統！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 帚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴 動手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼? 快給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快給我發射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成怎樣我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔喔~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千冬姐  帚  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及所有相關的人 我來守護！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亞 結束它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是賽西莉亞的話 一定能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何這樣就結…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告! 敵機IS再啟動確認! 已被鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹嘛呢 你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那兒慌慌張張個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有慌慌張張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡說 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台IS 怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 除了你沒有其他人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說古老肉那件事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是這樣的傍晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果廚藝變好了 你願意每天吃我做的古老肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次約定… 難道是有另外的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為是免費請我吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒錯 你想得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有人肯吃的話 廚藝不是會進步更快嗎 啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的古老肉當然也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過鈴的老爸的料理 還真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個 店…不會再開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我父母離婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會回國也是因為那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天我們去哪兒玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那也就是 約會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏同學 你身體怎麼樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來照顧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好在一夏醒過來之前是不能偷跑的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說這話的你 不是也在想偷跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏可是我的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說的話我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起你這個二班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 千冬姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還和我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是無人機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有登錄過的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS的核心世界上只有467個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個IS使用的核心卻並不在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的美少年 出現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 哪裡哪裡 到底在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國來的代表候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫 查理·德諾阿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面容姣好 性格和藹 頭腦優秀 而且非常強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千里挑一的好男生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.19,0:23:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他身上似乎隱藏著什麼秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:23:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boy Meets Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(260,250)\fs60}下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(640,480)\shad5\fs60}「Boy Meets Boy」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學以及德諾阿同學 兩人都好美型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來IS學園唸書 真是 太·好·了~
